    <item>
      <title>Cardiovascular problems are prevented by Vitamin D plus Omega-3</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/cardiovascular-problems-are-prevented-by-vitamin-d-plus-omega-3/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Feb 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/cardiovascular-problems-are-prevented-by-vitamin-d-plus-omega-3/</guid>
      <description>&lt;nav id=&#34;TableOfContents&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;ul&gt;&#xA;    &lt;li&gt;&#xA;      &lt;ul&gt;&#xA;        &lt;li&gt;&#xA;          &lt;ul&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#vitamin-d3-and-omega-3-fatty-acids-a-new-approach-for-cardiovascular-prevention&#34;&gt;Vitamin D3 and omega-3 fatty acids: A new approach for cardiovascular prevention&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#vitamindwiki---omega-3-helps-many-health-problemscategoriesvitamin-d-and-omega-3&#34;&gt;VitaminDWiki - &lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/categories/vitamin-d-and-omega-3&#34;&gt;Omega-3 helps many health problems&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;          &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/li&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/li&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;/nav&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h4 id=&#34;vitamin-d3-and-omega-3-fatty-acids-a-new-approach-for-cardiovascular-prevention&#34;&gt;Vitamin D3 and omega-3 fatty acids: A new approach for cardiovascular prevention&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Journal of Cardiovascular Pharmacology ():10.1097/FJC.0000000000001407, February 15, 2023. | DOI: 10.1097/FJC.0000000000001407&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Corcione, Nicola1,2; Biondi-Zoccai, Giuseppe3,4; Castellani, Valentina5; Carnevale, Roberto3,4&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The combination of vitamin D3 and omega-3 fatty acid has been shown to reduce oxidized low-density lipoprotein levels in patients with vitamin D deficiency. We hereby discuss the possible impact of supplementation with either or both for atherothrombosis prevention, and highlight their potentially beneficial impact for cardiovascular prevention.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
